OL,3,C'I've never felt so ill in my life':
OL,4,Cman urges vulnerable people to get flu
OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,FA 26-year-old man who spent 24 hours
OL,8,Fin hospital last Christmas is urging
OL,9,Fpeople to take their flu jabs this
OL,10,Fautumn.
OL,12,FJoseph Sullivan, from Cowbridge, who
OL,13,Fhas type 1 diabetes and auto-immune
OL,14,Fliver disease was hospitalised with
OL,15,Fthe flu in 2023 and said: "I've never
OL,16,Ffelt so ill in my entire life. I would
OL,17,Fnot wish it upon anyone."
