OL,3,C'I've never felt so ill in my life':
OL,4,Cman urges vulnerable people to get flu
OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,FPublic Health Wales has launched a
OL,8,Fcampaign to encourage eligible adults
OL,9,Fto come forward as soon as they have
OL,10,Fbeen contacted to receive their
OL,11,Fvaccination.
OL,13,FOver 467,000 people in Wales are said
OL,14,Fto be classed as clinically at risk
OL,15,Fand are therefore more vulnerable and
OL,16,Fmore likely to be significantly
OL,17,Fimpacted by the flu, according to the
OL,18,Fcampaign.
