OL,3,C'I've never felt so ill in my life':
OL,4,Cman urges vulnerable people to get flu
OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, Joseph
OL,8,Frecounted how he began to experience
OL,9,F"typical" symptoms in the run up to
OL,10,FChristmas last year, describing how he
OL,11,Ffelt "too hot, too cold",
OL,12,F"uncomfortable" and had "headaches".
OL,14,FBecause of his fever, Joseph took a
OL,15,Ffew days off from work.
