OL,3,C'I've never felt so ill in my life':
OL,4,Cman urges vulnerable people to get flu
OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,FHe said: "By the Thursday I thought I
OL,8,Fwas on the mend, but by Friday I had
OL,9,Fgone down hill massively. Because I'm
OL,10,Ftype one diabetic, my blood sugars get
OL,11,Fquite tricky to manage when I'm ill,
OL,12,Fso that didn't help either. I ended up
OL,13,Fgoing into A&E because of how rough I
OL,14,Fwas. I spent 24 hours there and
OL,15,Freceived fluids. I returned home on
OL,16,Fthe Saturday afternoon and then on
OL,17,FChristmas day itself I barely left my
OL,18,Fbed.
