OL,3,C'I've never felt so ill in my life':
OL,4,Cman urges vulnerable people to get flu
OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,F"It took me a couple of weeks to
OL,8,Fproperly recover, I think it was the
OL,9,Fstart of February when I was properly
OL,10,Fover it."
OL,12,FHealth officials are urging people
OL,13,Flike Joseph to take their flu jabs
OL,14,Fahead of this winter to protect them
OL,15,Ffrom secondary infections.
OL,17,FHe was one of nearly 2,000 people in
OL,18,FWales who were admitted to hospital
OL,19,Fwith flu in 2023.
