OL,3,C'I've never felt so ill in my life':
OL,4,Cman urges vulnerable people to get flu
OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,FLast year's figures show that nearly
OL,8,F75% of the over 65s got the jab,
OL,9,Fhowever, only 39% of those younger
OL,10,Fpeople from vulnerable groups had a
OL,11,Fflu vaccine.
OL,13,FGetting the vaccine can reduce the
OL,14,Fchances of people with long-term
OL,15,Fconditions being hospitalised from flu
OL,16,Fby up to a third according to Public
OL,17,FHealth Wales.
