OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,FFor an individual with liver disease,
OL,8,Fthe flu is 48 times more likely to be
OL,9,Ffatal, which causes concern for the
OL,10,F12,000 people in Wales living with the
OL,11,Fcondition.
OL,13,FThere are over 99,000 people living
OL,14,Fwith diabetes in Wales. They are 6
OL,15,Ftimes more likely to die from flu.
