OL,3,C'I've never felt so ill in my life':
OL,4,Cman urges vulnerable people to get flu
OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,FThis year, all school children will be
OL,8,Foffered the flu vaccine, as well as
OL,9,Ftwo and three year olds, those
OL,10,Fclinically at risk, those over 65 and
OL,11,Ffrontline health and social care
OL,12,Fworkers.
OL,14,FGPs and Health Boards will contact
OL,15,Fthose who are eligible with details of
OL,16,Fwhen and where they can be vaccinated.
