OL,3,C'I've never felt so ill in my life':
OL,4,Cman urges vulnerable people to get flu
OL,5,Cjab
OL,7,FDr Christopher Johnson, Head of Public
OL,8,FHealth Wales' Vaccine Preventable
OL,9,FDisease Programme said: "Many people
OL,10,Fwith common conditions like asthma or
OL,11,Fdiabetes may not consider themselves
OL,12,Fto be clinically at risk, but flu can
OL,13,Fbe serious for people with existing
OL,14,Fhealth conditions.
OL,16,F"It is well known that having a flu
OL,17,Fvaccine every year is one of the most
OL,18,Feffective ways to protect against flu.
OL,19,FAny side effects from the vaccinations
OL,20,Fare normally mild and don't last long."
